headline.main: LOUISA M. ALCOTT DEAD.; THE AUTHORESS DIES ON THE DAY OF HER FATHER'S FUNERAL.

snippet: BOSTON, Mass., March 6.--Miss Louisa M. Alcott died this morning. Coming so soon after the death of her father the suddenly announced decease of Miss Alcott brings a double sorrow to the many friends of the family, while the loss of this talented ...
